g.text: The Filter-Buttons are going to be dynamically added for all actual active Heuristics.
Therefore at the Attributes these Buttons are missing.
The Heuristics are given by the Controller.
The Properties are saved at the HeuristicProperties.
These Properties will be translated into the correct TextBoxes for the user to set the Properties with.
=> Most of the Attributes of the GUI-Elements are missing.
